text:
Hello Peeps i created a telegram book club group where we are going to read a book every two or three weeks and have a discussion about them. I am not much of a reader but i think being in a book club where i could talk to people about books would help me a lot and i think the same goes for most of us struggling to get into reading.

The Book Club is called

("the Akan God of Stories, Wisdom, Knowledge, and trickery"). Also the name of the group can be changed if you don't like it. The name does not matter that much.

Inspired by
